{"tid":940867,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"聽《L.O.V.E》之感受","createTime":"2018-12-14T09:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T10:52:30.000Z","uid":97036,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1783ff8e59142347d60b7baaaaa1177a01865b1a","tid":940867,"uid":97036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"1.\t《破壞王》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFunk曲風，《兩名男子街頭相遇》+《謝謝儂》嘅混合體，再睇返原來《兩名男子》都係王雙駿寫嘅，冇新意。<br />\n<br />\n2.\t《海裡睡人》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.\t《漸漸》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來都唔係好想講陳詠謙啲詞，但係呢份歌詞真係&hellip;&hellip; 好低質，好似啲業餘填詞咁。聽到最後果句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「渾噩哪及記得恐怖 記得種種感覺 但欠你的廝守到老」；</div></span><br />\n覺得怪怪地，上網揾左揾，陳詠謙究竟你有幾中意「廝守到老」？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「我最愛那個說未定現在還未到 還未夠早廝守到老」（《不一定》，劉浩龍）；<br />\n「讓你讓我回頭細看 即管看 廝守到老的曙光」（《回到當初》，梁漢文）；<br />\n「共你歷年尋新鮮 吃盡風沙 廝守到老亦毫不驚訝」（《我的宣言》，周柏豪）；</div></span><br />\n而且三首都係擺係成首歌嘅尾段/Bridge嘅部分，姐係代表陳填呢啲愛情題材，係佢嘅愛情世界入面，「廝守到老」就係最高潮，最高嘅境界，一個「專業填詞人」嘅用字用詞可以貧乏到咁。Eason感情演繹得好好，但低質嘅詞，影響到我聽歌嘅心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n4.\t《敬菸》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻碟小弟最中意嘅三首之一！<br />\n<br />\n5.\t《蠢》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇嘢好評。<br />\n<br />\n6.\t《瘋狂的朋友》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同上。<br />\n<br />\n7.\t《Run》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nYoyo寫俾Eason果首《Baby Song》幾好聽！（好多人覺得Baby Song係爸爸唱俾仔女聽，但我反而覺得係歌者唱返俾自己聽，鼓舞自己嘅歌。）<br />\n<br />\n8.\t《Tequila》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n9.\t《我們萬歲》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻碟小弟最中意嘅三首之一！<br />\n<br />\n10.\t《與你常在》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n《後台》、《歌頌》、《Allegro Opus 3.3 am》類型嘅歌，分別講幕後工作人員、作曲者、填詞人。《與你》就講表演樂隊，幾首入面呢首較差。<br />\n<br />\n11.\t《可一可再》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻碟小弟最中意嘅三首之一！初初聽果陣哼左成日，個旋律真係好上腦好正！但聽講宜家俾人話Eason抄歌？我聽左次係的確好似，但Eason都澄清左，而且態度都幾好啦，無謂再講，就算係告都係著作人告。（相反王雙駿首《我的世界末日》真係&hellip;&hellip;想聽佢親自解釋下）<br />\n<br />\n大家聽完又有咩感受？之前講過話《L.O.V.E》呢隻大碟質素好差，好似好多人唔同意。請指教。"},{"pid":"de310444a71688e5a37a45536183846fe4470d3c","tid":940867,"uid":16986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"Eason唱得唔洗講<br />\n有睇佢係中環個live都知佢把聲好fit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n編曲好出彩 <br />\n但衰在曲詞平庸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前Eason啲歌係愈聽愈有味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後勁凌厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢隻碟大部分歌第一次聽就朗朗上口<br />\n但好快唔想loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曲詞先係一首歌嘅根本無講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}